      • dominates

        public boolean dominates(Individual that)
        This method determines if an individual dominates another individual. An individual dominates another if he is no worse than the other in all objectives and strictly better in at least one.
        Parameters:
        that - The other individual to compare to.
        Returns:
        true if the individual dominates, false otherwise.
